node.title: PM Jacinda Ardern holding unscheduled press conference at 11am
node.description: It comes after she said if Omicron moves beyond the border the whole country would move to red within 24-48 hours.
node.content: ["Newshub understands the Prime minister is due to hold an unscheduled press conference at 11am\n", "This week the Prime Minister said if Omicron moves beyond the border the whole country would move to red within 24-48 hours.\u00a0", "This is breaking news - more to come."]
